=Introduction=

The Mass viewpoint enables to simply describe the non-functional aspect of mass in Capella.
It provides several capabilities:

* Definition of mass value to be associated with model elements
* Definition of maximum mass value to be associated with model elements
* Computation of model element mass value based on self mass value and child masse values
* Visualization of maximum mass value compliance with regards to computed value